description         MooseX::Has::Sugar - Sugar Syntax for moose 'has' fields

long_description    Moose has syntax is generally fine, but sometimes one \
                    gets bothered with the constant typing of string quotes \
                    for things. The MooseX::Types module exists and in many \
                    ways reduces the need for constant string creation.

